## Non-Seeds And Inert Decorations

### 1. Exact duplicate of the first triad

- `[INFERRED]` If
  `c = b`,
  then `T_2 = T_1`.
  That is not a new second-budget seed.
- `[INFERRED]` Adding another helical sign sector on the same one-triad
